 has two children lily and willoughby christian b  robinson is a recovering alcoholic having stopped drinking in  he relapsed before and during the filming of the rum diary but stopped drinking again after the film was finished filmographyedit actingedit romeo and juliet  the other people  the music lovers  tamlin  private road  los viajes escolares  the story of adele h  kleinhoff hotel  the brute  still crazy  directingedit withnail and i  how to get ahead in advertising  jennifer   the rum diary  screenwritingedit the killing fields  withnail and i  how to get ahead in advertising  fat man and little boy  jennifer   return to paradise  in dreams  the rum diary  bibliographyedit paranoia in the launderette  the peculiar memories of thomas penman  the obvious elephant  harold and the duck  they all love jack busting the ripper  referencesedit  interview by robert chalmers  february  the independent on sunday the new review p  february  independentcouk retrieved  february    httpwwwtelegraphcouknewsuknewscrimejacktherippermysterysolvedhtml  jack the ripper has bruce robinson solved the worlds most famous crime the telegraph retrieved  october    how one man revealed jack the rippers identity the full story gq retrieved  october    bfi screenonline withnail and i  screenonlineorguk retrieved  february    russell jamie films article article – how withnail  i became a cult bbc retrieved  february    bfi screenonline robinson bruce – biography screenonlineorguk  may  retrieved  february    bruce robinson  britmovie  home of british films britmovie retrieved  february    withnails bruce robinson to direct the rum diary  movie news  empire empireonlinecom  december  retrieved  february    the rum diary now filming ign  april  retrieved  august    chalmers robert  february  bruce robinson i started drinking again because of the rum diary the independent retrieved  february   external linksedit wikiquote has quotations related to bruce robinson bruce robinson on imdb bruce 